    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>Description here</p></blockquote><p>Hello World.</p><p>A paragraph is a number of sentences grouped together and relating to one topic. Or, a group of related sentences that develop a single point.<a id="more"></a> This definition shows that the paragraphs of compositions are not mere arbitrary divisions. The division of a chapter into paragraphs must be made according to the changes of ideas introduced.</p>]]></content>
    
    
